{"tid":2402683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃絲陳潔玲網店hkfoodbuyer同綠店「點點鮮」係咩合作關係？","createTime":"2021-02-10T14:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T02:34:18.000Z","uid":66881,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a8eea88ec7da3ec6c012ee242fbe16404b5feaa7","tid":2402683,"uid":66881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"陳潔玲間網店hkfoodbuyer海鮮嗰頁全部都係「點點鮮」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqVzJU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqVzJU2.png&h=e112680b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zii5Qz2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzii5Qz2.png&h=81684454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而點點鮮上年6月就因為TVB東張西望落廣告<br />\n由黃店俾人踢左去綠店<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/3zFFOwQhp1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F3zFFOwQhp1%2F&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGheu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=f41c8f8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/3zFFOwQhp1/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100226174720726/posts/353919732684701/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100226174720726%2Fposts%2F353919732684701%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGheu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=42f20ca2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100226174720726/posts/353919732684701/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再睇返前少少<br />\n<br />\n點點鮮本身係同莊端兒合作開，係黃店<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SUrGo0p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSUrGo0p.png&h=f263cb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳潔玲又喺2020年暑假<br />\n同莊端兒肥腸合作搞直播「表姐有好嘢」賣嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xURnSR5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxURnSR5.png&h=f4f8e5d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾「表姐有好嘢」又突然唔見左莊端兒同肥腸<br />\n變成左依條女「自己新開嘅網店」<br />\n成個ig ac得返陳潔玲自己<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UnETZxy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUnETZxy.png&h=496b5c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一時間莊端兒都無再出現喺點點鮮<br />\n幾個月之後陳潔玲開左間hkfoodbuyer<br />\n入面就大量點點鮮嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n成個過程都好耐人尋味"},{"pid":"402091079f87ca56bf97af63d4f52738d95313ab","tid":2402683,"uid":135922,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"又準備開始批鬥？"},{"pid":"e4d8886f2c1c0cb3fb5bcbc32d1011ea856ad688","tid":2402683,"uid":66881,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"402091079f87ca56bf97af63d4f52738d95313ab","tid":2402683,"uid":135922,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:37:02.000Z","msg":"又準備開始批鬥？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"問個清楚問個明白啫"},{"pid":"0bfa2bf6baf88b2ea82c872e1ef08ce990d4b1b8","tid":2402683,"uid":44061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"批鬥post 拉"},{"pid":"0581e2a51ec383ade2d6931bac9d798457739dbd","tid":2402683,"uid":137569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"樓主係hktv mall pr<br />\n帶風向"},{"pid":"d60475050033ac129654f8e1912460857d492e9f","tid":2402683,"uid":66881,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0581e2a51ec383ade2d6931bac9d798457739dbd","tid":2402683,"uid":137569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"樓主係hktv mall pr<br />\n帶風向"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"其實你係咪點點鮮或者陳潔玲Pr？"},{"pid":"d6b4196c0e9c596e8f6a8fcec9ac371fafa2a5fa","tid":2402683,"uid":19557,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d60475050033ac129654f8e1912460857d492e9f","tid":2402683,"uid":66881,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0581e2a51ec383ade2d6931bac9d798457739dbd","tid":2402683,"uid":137569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:46:21.000Z","msg":"樓主係hktv mall pr<br />\n帶風向"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"其實你係咪點點鮮或者陳潔玲Pr？"}